---

<section class="about" id="about-section">
  <div class="inner">
    <p class="label">// about</p>
    <div class="content">
      <p>
        I build <span class="highlight">full stack products</span> that scale, from architecture to deployment.
        I've shipped web apps, mobile apps (iOS and Android), and serverless APIs across startups and product teams.
      </p>
      <p>
        Right now I'm at <span class="highlight">PeopleCor</span>, where I own core platform features and lead our
        <span class="highlight">AI developer tooling</span> initiative using Claude SDD and CodeRabbit.
      </p>
      <p>
        Based in <span class="highlight">Mexico City</span>. Open to remote opportunities worldwide.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="meta">
      <div class="meta-item">
        <span class="meta-value">9+</span>
        <span class="meta-label">years experience</span>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-item">
        <span class="meta-value">10+</span>
        <span class="meta-label">products shipped</span>
      </div>
      <div class="meta-item">
        <span class="meta-value">iOS + Android</span>
        <span class="meta-label">mobile apps published</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about {
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  .inner {
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 3rem 1.5rem;
  }

  .label {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 11px;
    color: var(--accent-green);
    letter-spacing: 3px;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
  }

  .content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
    max-width: 620px;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .content p {
    font-size: 15px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .highlight {
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .meta {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1rem;
  }

  .meta-item {
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 4px;
  }

  .meta-value {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 20px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--accent-blue);
  }

  .meta-label {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--text-secondary);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .meta {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>